731
00:38:23,982 --> 00:38:25,315
Oh, I don't mind, you know.

732
00:38:25,316 --> 00:38:27,834
Hmm. Beats workin'.

733
00:38:31,406 --> 00:38:32,672
Uh...

734
00:38:34,951 --> 00:38:37,119
