753
00:39:30,131 --> 00:39:32,299
You down there.

754
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:36,261
The old man who lived downstairs says he
heard the kid yell out, "I'm gonna kill ya."

755
00:39:36,262 --> 00:39:38,972
