The window was open.

761
00:39:49,984 --> 00:39:51,902
So was the one upstairs.
It was a hot night, remember?

762
00:39:51,903 --> 00:39:53,320
Well, it was another apartment.

763
00:39:53,321 --> 00:39:55,989
