1250
01:04:09,150 --> 01:04:12,778
- Yeah. Well, good luck.
- Oh, come on. You're like everybody else.

1251
01:04:12,779 --> 01:04:15,088
You think too much.
You get mixed up.

1252
01:04:16,241 --> 01:04:17,373
You know what I mean?

1253
01:04:17,399 --> 01:04:20,285
Now, listen. I don't think
you have any right...

1254
