01:05:15,592 --> 01:05:18,193
Look at that come down, will you?

1256
01:05:19,262 --> 01:05:21,221
You know...

1257
01:05:21,222 --> 01:05:23,807
this reminds me of a
storm we had last...

1258
01:05:23,808 --> 01:05:27,352
