1369
01:11:03,522 --> 01:11:06,232
The, um...

1370
01:11:06,233 --> 01:11:08,985
I'll tell you in a minute.
The, uh...

1371
01:11:08,986 --> 01:11:13,239
Remarkable Mrs., uh, something...

1372
01:11:13,240 --> 01:11:15,784
The...

1373
01:11:15,785 --> 01:11:18,536
Mrs. Bainbridge.
